1
00:00:36,359 --> 00:00:37,280
Stop moving things.

2
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:39,520
Why are you being so unreasonable?

3
00:00:41,119 --> 00:00:41,719
No way.

4
00:00:41,719 --> 00:00:42,240
Give it back.

5
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:43,359
I've lived in this home for half my life.

6
00:00:43,359 --> 00:00:44,719
If we don't live here, where will we go?

7
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:46,320
I don't care where you live.

8
00:00:46,399 --> 00:00:48,600
Either pay up or give us the house.

9
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:49,799
Mom!

10
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:51,000
Mom!

11
00:00:51,359 --> 00:00:51,960
What are you doing?

12
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:52,439
Auntie.

13
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:53,359
Auntie.

14
00:00:53,719 --> 00:00:55,880
Can't you give us a little more time?

15
00:00:55,920 --> 00:00:57,079
Can you even afford to pay it back?

16
00:00:57,119 --> 00:00:58,479
I doubt you can even cover the interest.

17
00:00:59,359 --> 00:01:00,159
How could I...

18
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,399
Try to welch on the debt?

19
00:01:04,519 --> 00:01:05,519
You three.

20
00:01:05,640 --> 00:01:07,239
Why do you watch them get bullied...

21
00:01:07,239 --> 00:01:08,280
...and do nothing about it?

22
00:01:13,519 --> 00:01:14,280
Mom.

23
00:01:14,599 --> 00:01:16,000
The money I asked you to keep for me...

24
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:16,920
Give it to me first.

25
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:18,079
Okay, just wait.

26
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:18,799
Stay out of this.

27
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:21,079
Don't move.

28
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:27,120
Mom, are you okay?

29
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:28,640
Eldest, here.

30
00:01:29,359 --> 00:01:30,319
I added a little.

31
00:01:30,719 --> 00:01:31,680
There's ten thousand in total inside.

32
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,200
Here is ten thousand yuan.

33
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:45,079
Whether it's for the principal...

34
00:01:45,079 --> 00:01:46,000
...or the interest.

35
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:48,079
Buying us another month of time...

36
00:01:48,079 --> 00:01:49,079
...should be enough, right?

37
00:01:50,319 --> 00:01:51,079
Fine.

38
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:52,120
One month, then.

39
00:01:52,319 --> 00:01:53,079
Let's go.

40
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:01,879
Let's tidy up first.

41
00:02:02,439 --> 00:02:03,400
It's okay, it's okay.

42
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:07,519
Mom, it's all over now.

43
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,800
They're gone.

44
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,759
Mom.

45
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:12,039
Over this period...

46
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,719
...I've saved up some of my wages.

47
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:14,919
I'll check in a bit...

48
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,120
...to see how much is left.

49
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:17,439
Mom.

50
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:19,840
My vinegar workshop can spare some money too.

51
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,000
Don't worry anymore.

52
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,199
We'll solve this.

53
00:02:28,879 --> 00:02:29,680
Yingrong.

54
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:33,719
Yingzhu.

55
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,680
As a mother...

56
00:02:37,039 --> 00:02:38,680
...I was wrong.

57
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,280
Terribly wrong.

58
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,360
Mom.

59
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:43,759
We are a family.

60
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:45,000
There is no right or wrong between us.

61
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,960
As long as our hearts are together...

62
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,879
...we can overcome any difficulty.

63
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:50,840
Yingrong.

64
00:02:51,319 --> 00:02:52,319
All these years...

65
00:02:52,599 --> 00:02:54,199
...it hasn't been easy for you.

66
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:57,520
You've always been protecting this family.

67
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:01,280
And Mom has always been blaming you.

68
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:06,919
Mom.

69
00:03:07,319 --> 00:03:08,599
It's okay.

70
00:03:16,319 --> 00:03:18,199
It's okay. Don't cry.

71
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:37,240
Xuelin.

72
00:03:37,319 --> 00:03:38,319
Thank you.

73
00:03:38,879 --> 00:03:40,360
What are you saying?

74
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,599
We're neighbors.

75
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,319
Why wouldn't I help out?

76
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,479
I don't know when

77
00:04:02,479 --> 00:04:03,080
it was put here.

78
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,199
I'll put it away.

79
00:04:05,439 --> 00:04:06,479
I know.

80
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:08,520
You didn't want me to see it.

81
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,919
Didn't want to upset me.

82
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,479
But...

83
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,120
look at this.

84
00:04:14,439 --> 00:04:15,520
Back then,

85
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:18,959
how close our two families were.

86
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,279
Xuelin!

87
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,319
Time to eat! Time to eat!

88
00:04:22,319 --> 00:04:23,560
Coming!

89
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,040
Food is here!

90
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:24,720
Sit down, sit down.

91
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:25,399
Make way.

92
00:04:25,759 --> 00:04:26,839
Here comes the dish.

93
00:04:26,959 --> 00:04:27,360
Sit down, sit down.

94
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,240
I'll get it, I'll get it.

95
00:04:28,959 --> 00:04:30,839
It looks delicious, Auntie.

96
00:04:30,839 --> 00:04:31,480
Come, make some room.

97
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,480
Eat plenty later.

98
00:04:33,839 --> 00:04:34,519
Come on.

99
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:35,199
Come, come, come.

100
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:36,439
Come on.

101
00:04:36,439 --> 00:04:37,000
Open wide.

102
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:38,759
Come on.

103
00:04:39,519 --> 00:04:40,480
In the blink of an eye,

104
00:04:41,439 --> 00:04:44,439
so many years have passed.

105
00:04:45,079 --> 00:04:46,040
Xuelin,

106
00:04:46,199 --> 00:04:47,519
it hasn't been easy for you.

107
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:49,639
Raising sons and daughters...

108
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,120
none of it is easy.

109
00:04:51,839 --> 00:04:52,800
It's the same for you.

110
00:04:53,879 --> 00:04:54,920
I know.

111
00:04:55,439 --> 00:04:56,240
All these years,

112
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:59,839
you've always felt guilty towards us.

113
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:02,480
That's why you tolerated me.

114
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:04,879
And I...

115
00:05:04,879 --> 00:05:06,439
kept making things hard for you.

116
00:05:06,879 --> 00:05:08,279
You were angry inside.

117
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:09,480
I know that.

118
00:05:09,879 --> 00:05:10,879
Besides,

119
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,879
who was putting up with your temper?

120
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:16,639
We've argued plenty over the years, haven't we?

121
00:05:19,079 --> 00:05:20,079
Back then,

122
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:21,800
Jianshe...

123
00:05:21,879 --> 00:05:24,800
swapped shifts just to celebrate my birthday.

124
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,720
Actually,

125
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,720
I've always known

126
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:31,160
that it was an accident.

127
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:34,480
But I kept blaming your Wang family.

128
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:40,199
I didn't dare think about it.

129
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:45,279
If I didn't have someone to scold,

130
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:46,920
to blame,

131
00:05:47,519 --> 00:05:48,800
inside my heart,

132
00:05:49,319 --> 00:05:50,680
I couldn't have borne it.

133
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:53,920
Xuelin,

134
00:05:55,879 --> 00:05:57,720
life has its bitterness and sweetness.

135
00:05:57,839 --> 00:06:00,079
You can't just look at the bitter side.

136
00:06:00,839 --> 00:06:03,399
Now your three sons are so sensible.

137
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:05,839
There will be good times ahead.

138
00:06:09,279 --> 00:06:10,920
Let's live a good life together.

139
00:06:11,279 --> 00:06:12,839
Our two families together...

140
00:06:13,519 --> 00:06:16,920
will definitely live a good life.

141
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,519
How wonderful

142
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:35,839
Xuelin

143
00:06:36,079 --> 00:06:37,639
Your family is going to strike it rich

144
00:06:38,079 --> 00:06:39,560
That new rich family, the Fangs, said

145
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:41,279
they're coming to find your son

146
00:06:42,439 --> 00:06:43,279
Sister Chen

147
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:44,600
Are you pulling my leg?

148
00:06:45,279 --> 00:06:46,839
This time they're really looking for you

149
00:06:46,879 --> 00:06:48,279
I asked and made sure

150
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:52,439
Are you Big Sister Xuelin?

151
00:06:52,439 --> 00:06:53,199
I am

152
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:55,079
Are you really looking for me?

153
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,560
You didn't get the wrong person, right?

154
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,439
Is Zheng Haiyang your son?

155
00:06:59,759 --> 00:07:00,560
Yes

156
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:02,199
Then there's no mistake

157
00:07:03,279 --> 00:07:04,439
This is my daughter

158
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:05,279
Her name is Fang Fang

159
00:07:05,879 --> 00:07:08,560
She has taken a fancy to your Haiyang

160
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:09,560
Dad

161
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,879
We're here this time to propose a marriage

162
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:14,399
This is a gift for Haiyang

163
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,399
The daughter of the new rich

164
00:07:15,399 --> 00:07:16,079
has taken a fancy to their second son

165
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,399
Let's go inside and talk

166
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:18,800
Okay

167
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,040
Let's chat inside

168
00:07:20,399 --> 00:07:21,199
Okay

169
00:07:22,839 --> 00:07:24,480
They are going to strike it rich

170
00:07:25,439 --> 00:07:26,560
Did I hear that right?

171
00:07:27,279 --> 00:07:28,759
This new rich family

172
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:30,639
actually took a fancy to Zheng Haiyang

173
00:07:30,839 --> 00:07:31,839
Then won't Zheng Haiyang

174
00:07:31,839 --> 00:07:34,000
become the son-in-law of the new rich?

175
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,199
That's really great

176
00:07:37,199 --> 00:07:38,879
These things are so nice

177
00:07:40,079 --> 00:07:40,839
I don't agree

178
00:07:40,839 --> 00:07:41,839
What did you say?

179
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,879
That Fang family is the new rich

180
00:07:45,519 --> 00:07:47,040
Their daughter likes you

181
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,319
and doesn't mind that you've been in the slammer

182
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,839
What is there to disagree with?

183
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,160
I don't like her

184
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:52,560
I have no feelings for her

185
00:07:54,199 --> 00:07:55,639
You fool

186
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:57,399
Stay out of this matter

187
00:07:57,399 --> 00:07:58,639
Do as I say

188
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,000
Get engaged first

189
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,480
Secure the title first

190
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:03,240
You can develop feelings later

191
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,839
Isn't that perfectly justifiable?

192
00:08:05,199 --> 00:08:06,800
We can't do things this way

193
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,600
I'll go make it clear to Fang Fang tomorrow

194
00:08:09,639 --> 00:08:11,519
Fang Fang has already chosen you

195
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,639
Stop making a fuss

196
00:08:12,839 --> 00:08:14,279
Why not just be friends first?

197
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:16,519
Isn't this Li Guangming?

198
00:08:16,519 --> 00:08:17,560
I didn't engage in profiteering

199
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,879
I didn't make fake wine

200
00:08:20,519 --> 00:08:21,160
Boss Tang

201
00:08:21,319 --> 00:08:21,959
Boss Tang

202
00:08:21,959 --> 00:08:23,279
I'll pay back the money, I definitely will

203
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,639
You're just a scoundrel

204
00:08:24,639 --> 00:08:26,040
Like I'd believe your nonsense

205
00:08:26,199 --> 00:08:27,000
Boss Tang, give me a chance

206
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:27,600
Yingrong

207
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:28,240
Yingrong

208
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,079
Yingzhu

209
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,920
Yingzhu, save me, Yingzhu

210
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:31,680
Yingzhu, save me

211
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,639
Yingzhu

212
00:08:32,639 --> 00:08:33,559
I'm your husband

213
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,840
I am your husband

214
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,000
I'm your husband

215
00:08:36,279 --> 00:08:37,759
We are already divorced

216
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:38,679
The way you are now

217
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:40,279
is entirely your own doing

218
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:40,919
Yingzhu, you...

219
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,759
Yingzhu, just you wait

220
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:44,879
Wang Yingrong

221
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:45,679
Zheng Minjiang

222
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,559
It's all your fault I ended up like this

223
00:08:47,559 --> 00:08:49,159
I will never let you off

224
00:08:49,159 --> 00:08:50,840
I will never let you off

225
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,120
Serves him right

226
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:56,919
Good riddance

227
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:58,799
Minjiang

228
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:01,480
Boss Tang

229
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,759
What's going on with Li Guangming?

230
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:06,000
This guy owes a ton of debt

231
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:08,279
He made fake wine that sent people to the hospital

232
00:09:08,279 --> 00:09:09,399
I advised him out of kindness

233
00:09:09,399 --> 00:09:11,679
but he grabbed a shovel to resist the law

234
00:09:12,279 --> 00:09:14,120
He really brought it on himself

235
00:09:16,639 --> 00:09:17,679
Teacher Zhen

236
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:20,080
We welcome leaders of all levels at any time

237
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,840
to visit and inspect Baliang Vinegar Workshop

238
00:09:21,879 --> 00:09:22,919
Go take a look

239
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,360
Sit, sit, sit

240
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:31,279
Currently, Baliang Vinegar Workshop

241
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:33,360
has been affiliated with

242
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:35,279
the production line of the State-owned Vinegar Factory.

243
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:38,200
The procedures for external sales

244
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:41,080
are also gradually being approved.

245
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,480
Selling vinegar through state affiliation

246
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:44,120
is just a stopgap measure for us.

247
00:09:44,159 --> 00:09:46,480
We still want to strive to be the first batch

248
00:09:46,559 --> 00:09:48,879
to obtain the Private Vinegar Workshop Operating License.

249
00:09:48,879 --> 00:09:49,840
That five percent...

250
00:09:49,919 --> 00:09:51,200
for greater possibilities for the brand,

251
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,480
and to be fully prepared.

252
00:09:53,039 --> 00:09:55,080
We want to be the trailblazers.

253
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:57,840
Well, regarding this operating license,

254
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,679
the time it takes to get approved and processed

255
00:09:59,679 --> 00:10:00,600
is uncertain.

256
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:03,200
It could be a few months,

257
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:05,639
or it could be a few years.

258
00:10:06,279 --> 00:10:08,200
No matter how many years these procedures take,

259
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,399
I will not give up.

260
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,440
Perhaps reform

261
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:17,080
relies on young people like you

262
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,480
to explore the way forward.

263
00:10:20,039 --> 00:10:20,840
All right.

264
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,240
Go back and wait for news.

265
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:29,639
Uncle Zhen,

266
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:32,080
Zhen Zhen's leg was injured because of me.

267
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,799
You are still willing to help me like this,

268
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,399
I am very grateful,

269
00:10:35,559 --> 00:10:37,080
and also very guilty.

270
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:40,039
I haven't found a chance to apologize to you before.

271
00:10:42,919 --> 00:10:43,720
I'm sorry.

272
00:10:51,399 --> 00:10:52,200
Teacher.

273
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:55,120
This time it was my mom's fault.

274
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,080
I am her son.

275
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:58,840
If

276
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:00,919
there is anything Zhen Zhen or you need me to do,

277
00:11:01,399 --> 00:11:03,480
I am willing to take full responsibility.

278
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:08,440
Making you my son-in-law...

279
00:11:09,039 --> 00:11:09,879
would you be willing?

280
00:11:10,159 --> 00:11:11,120
Anything except that.

281
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,080
You...

282
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,480
Zhen Zhen getting injured

283
00:11:19,159 --> 00:11:20,840
does indeed make my heart ache.

284
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,639
But I also know very clearly

285
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:23,840
that this was an accident.

286
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:26,399
No one wanted it to happen.

287
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,039
You kid,

288
00:11:29,159 --> 00:11:31,000
you make people grit their teeth in anger,

289
00:11:31,679 --> 00:11:33,039
yet you are also very likable.

290
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:35,080
I speak from experience.

291
00:11:36,799 --> 00:11:39,720
If you don't like my daughter,

